  </div></div><h2>1. Eleken for SaaS and product-driven startups</h2><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680ba229179a8893ae619818_1%20(1).png" loading="lazy" alt="Eleken UI/UX design agency"/></div></figure><p><a href="../index.html"><strong>Eleken</strong></a><strong> is a UI/UX design agency 100% focused on SaaS products.</strong> Our designers don’t just create a polished <a href="application-interface-design-examples-how-top-companies-design-their-apps-uis">application interface design</a>. They conduct user interviews, analyze behavior, and turn early-stage ideas into clean, mobile-first experiences built around real user needs.</p><ul role="list"><li><strong>Founded</strong>: 2015</li><li><strong>Key services</strong>: SaaS product discovery and research, creating mockups, design from scratch, product redesign</li><li><strong>Collaboration model</strong>: Remote team, global clients</li><li><strong>Industry focus</strong>: SaaS, with expertise in fintech, healthcare,  sales, marketing, and designing complex, data-driven mobile apps that involve geospatial data, GIS, AI, satellite imagery, and deep data visualization.</li></ul><p>We follow a <strong>dedicated designer model</strong>, meaning you get a full-time product <a href="ui-ux-designer-vs-front-end-developer">UI/UX designer</a> working as part of your in-house team. There is no juggling between projects and handoffs; just one expert focuses entirely on your product.</p><p>All Eleken designers are also trained as project managers. That means they design and lead the work from start to finish, driving clarity, speed, and results without additional coordination overhead. </p><p>From <a href="time-tracking-app-design-how-to-make-an-app-that-increases-productivity">time tracking app design</a> to enterprise dashboards, we help SaaS teams turn complex workflows into clean, intuitive experiences.</p><p>Want to see how we work? Check out our ultimate SaaS product design approach in this video:</p><figure style="padding-bottom:56.206088992974244%" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-video"><div><iframe allowfullscreen="true" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BkN9__XaeSo?start=2" title="Eleken&#x27;s Ultimate SaaS Product Design Approach"></iframe></div></figure><h4>Clutch rating + client reviews</h4><p>Eleken is rated <a href="https://clutch.co/profile/eleken">4.9 on Clutch from 100+ SaaS clients</a>.</p><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680ba2d3012400ac80df5529_2%20(1).png" loading="lazy" alt="Eleken client reviews"/></div></figure><p><strong>Strong points:</strong></p><ul role="list"><li>Fast delivery with results that clients can track</li></ul><figure style="max-width:undefinedpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680ba4d03a4bf6c636292c6d_3%20(1).png" loading="lazy" alt="Eleken client reviews"/></div></figure><ul role="list"><li>Deep SaaS expertise</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680ba4fcf06ec0c32bce66f9_4%20(1).png" loading="lazy" alt="Eleken client reviews"/></div></figure><ul role="list"><li>Transparent pricing</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680ba5144fc613c4898190ac_5.png" loading="lazy" alt="Eleken client reviews"/></div></figure><ul role="list"><li>No fluff and middlemen</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fu