  </div></div><h2>2. Ramotion</h2><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680ba58c2f1c16734f3d40c9_8%20(1).png" loading="lazy" alt="Ramotion"/></div></figure><p><a href="https://www.ramotion.com/"><strong>Ramotion</strong></a><strong> is a US-based app design company that blends brand strategy with mobile app design and development. </strong>This combination especially appeals to funded startups and tech companies aiming to differentiate through design. It is also among the <a href="popular-web-design-companies">popular web design companies</a>.</p><h4><strong>Overview</strong></h4><ul role="list"><li><strong>Founded</strong>: 2009</li><li><strong>Key services</strong>: Branding, design, and development</li><li><strong>Collaboration model</strong>: Distributed team</li><li><strong>Industry focus</strong>: Healthcare, fintech, cybersecurity, B2B, SaaS</li></ul><p>Ramotion’s mobile design process is tightly connected to front-end development, which allows for high design fidelity and consistent user experiences across iOS and Android. </p><h4>Clutch rating + client reviews</h4><p>Ramotion’s portfolio includes work for companies like Redis, Cypress, and Crunchbase.</p><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680ba59f39d86ee0d66cf0f4_9.png" loading="lazy" alt="Clients"/></div></figure><p><strong>Clutch rating is </strong>4.9 based on 28 reviews.</p><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680ba5c2bda3d9f43b23218b_10.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency client reviews"/></div></figure><p><strong>Strong points:</strong></p><ul role="list"><li>Great brand + design com