  </div></div><h2>9. Appinventiv</h2><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f69e52202d6f13d17e9df_61.png" loading="lazy" alt="Appinventiv"/></div></figure><p><a href="https://appinventiv.com/"><strong>Appinventiv</strong></a><strong> is a large-scale, India-based </strong>app designing company<strong> with over 1,600 team members.</strong> It is a full-stack giant and a solid pick if you want scale or need a team that can go from concept to launch at volume.</p><h4><strong>Overview</strong></h4><ul role="list"><li><strong>Founded</strong>: 2015</li><li><strong>Key services</strong>: Design, development, and post-launch support</li><li><strong>Collaboration model</strong>: Global team</li><li><strong>Industry focus</strong>: Fintech, healthcare, eCommerce, and logistics</li></ul><p>Appinventiv is particularly well-suited for companies with big visions and complex requirements. While its scale allows it to take on large projects, it also means clients should expect a structured, process-heavy approach.</p><h4>Clutch rating + client reviews</h4><p>The company’s portfolio includes working with clients across the US, Europe, and MENA, such as IKEA, Google, KFC, and more.</p><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f57f349ce3c7f223111ed_62.png" loading="lazy" alt="Clients"/></div></figure><p>Appinventiv has an overall review rating of <a href="https://clutch.co/profile/appinventiv#reviews">4.7 based on 86 client reviews on Clutch</a>.</p><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f58061328a59590000442_63.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><p><strong>Strong points:</strong></p><ul role="list"><li>Full-cycle product development</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f58168b4a65f94111d394_64.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><ul role="list"><li>Can handle large, complex projects at scale</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f5825aba6e07572f455f4_65.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><p><strong>Weak points:</strong></p><ul role="list"><li>Occasional miscommunication</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f5831bcbc7a584f5901e4_66.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><ul role="list"><li>Not ideal for tight collaboration</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f5843ebbbc195161ea27f_67.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><ul role="list"><li>Less suited to design-first or iterative teams</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f585261f880d75ae052e8_68.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><h4>Pricing and fit</h4><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f58644e37a92657ab55c6_69.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency pricing"/></div></figure><p>Appinventiv offers a <strong>project-based pricing model</strong> and is built to handle large-scale, technically demanding mobile apps:</p><ul role="list"><li><strong>Typical project cost:</strong> Starts at <strong>$50 K.</strong><br/><br/></li><li>Strong focus on full-cycle delivery, from design to backend architecture.<br/><br/></li></ul><p><strong>Appinventiv is a great fit for:</strong></p><ul role="list"><li>Scale-ups and funded startups looking for full-service execution.<br/><br/></li><li>Teams building mobile apps with complex backend requirements.<br/><br/></li><li>Companies that need robust technical teams and long-term support.</li></ul><h2>10. Algoworks</h2><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f5876d895ade01c2649d5_70.png" loading="lazy" alt=" Algoworks"/></div></figure><p><a href="https://www.algoworks.com/">Algoworks</a> <strong>is a global digital agency based in the US and India. It offers mobile app design and development, focusing on enterprise solutions. </strong>Its services span UI/UX design, native and cross-platform development, and deep integration with CRM and cloud platforms like Salesforce and AWS.</p><h4><strong>Overview</strong></h4><ul role="list"><li><strong>Founded</strong>: 2006</li><li><strong>Key services</strong>: Native iOS and Android app design agency, cross-platform development (React Native, Flutter), scalable enterprise app solutions</li><li><strong>Collaboration model</strong>: Global team</li><li><strong>Industry focus</strong>: Finance, logistics, retail, and healthcare</li></ul><p>With over 500 experts on its team, Algoworks is known for its highly structured process, which makes it a good fit for companies that need technical execution over design innovation.</p><h4>Clutch rating + client reviews</h4><p>The company is proud to have successfully developed 500+ apps for startups and Fortune 500 companies. Its<a href="https://clutch.co/profile/algoworks#reviews"> overall review rating on Clutch is 4.9</a>.</p><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f588d80c14264ae4b9fc2_71.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><p><strong>Strong points:</strong></p><ul role="list"><li>Technical depth and large-scale delivery capacity</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f589d80c14264ae4ba2aa_72.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><ul role="list"><li>Extensive Salesforce and cloud integration experience</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f58ab23620848b633f7a2_73.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><ul role="list"><li>Reliable process and consistent project management</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f58ba1ee901693c672586_74.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><p><strong>Weak points:</strong></p><ul role="list"><li>More dev-focused than design-driven, not ideal for teams seeking standout UX</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f58c61ee901693c67329c_75.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><ul role="list"><li>Communication and time zone gaps can be a challenge for US-based startups</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f58d81f2c8c713c826b82_76.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><ul role="list"><li>Documentation process</li></ul><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f58ed23620848b634396e_77.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><h4>Pricing and fit</h4><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f590163c4afbe1eb9961e_78.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agency reviews"/></div></figure><p>Algoworks uses a <strong>project-based pricing model</strong> with a strong emphasis on technical integration and backend systems:</p><ul role="list"><li><strong>Typical project cost:</strong> The mobile app development package starts at <strong>$3 K/month</strong>, while the minimal project size is<strong> $10 K</strong>.<br/><br/></li><li>Specializes in Salesforce, AWS, and other enterprise backend integrations.<br/><br/></li><li>Offers both design and development, with deep technical execution.<br/><br/></li></ul><p><strong>Algoworks is a good fit for:</strong></p><ul role="list"><li>Enterprises needing mobile apps tightly integrated with backend systems or CRM platforms.<br/><br/></li><li>Teams working with <strong>CRM platforms</strong> or internal tools.<br/><br/></li><li>Companies requiring technical depth more than front-end design innovation.</li></ul><h2>Comparison table</h2><p>If you&#x27;re the “just show me the options” type, here’s a quick breakdown of everything we just covered:</p><figure style="max-width:1999pxpx" class="w-richtext-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/680f59134ea052496dd7222b_79.png" loading="lazy" alt="Mobile app design agencies comparison"/></div></figure><div class="w-embed"><div class="banner-wrap banner">
