  </div></div><h2>Final thoughts </h2><p>Hiring a mobile app design firm can be a game-changer. Or it can be a money pit. It all depends on whether you’re solving the right problem at the right time with the right team.</p><p>So here’s what to consider:</p><ul role="list"><li>Don’t hire an agency if you don’t actually need an app.<br/><br/></li><li>Design is strategy. It’s UX. It’s UI. It’s not just Figma files.<br/><br/></li><li>Most serious agencies won’t even blink at projects under $10 K.<br/><br/></li></ul><p>If you’re a <strong>SaaS company that needs product thinking and design</strong> that moves the needle, <a href="../contact-us">contact Eleken</a>. We’ll tell you if we’re not the right fit. But if we are, we’ll make sure your app is something users want to choose and use.</p></div></div><div class="author-blog-wrap"><div class="author-card"><div class="author-card-title">written by:</div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/646f5cb8b183ec58f3a7d014_Natalia.png" loading="lazy" alt="image" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/646f5cb8b183ec58f3a7d014_Natalia-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/646f5cb8b183ec58f3a7d014_Natalia-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/646f5cb8b183ec58f3a7d014_Natalia.png 928w" class="author-card-img"/><a href="../author/natalia-yanchiy" class="auth-link-page w-inline-block"><div class="author-card-auth-name">Natalia Yanchiy</div></a><p class="author-card-bio">Experienced technical copywriter and content creator with a solid background in digital marketing. In collaboration with UI/UX designers, Natalia creates engaging and easily digestible content for growing SaaS companies.</p><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/natalia-yanchiy-07729883/" target="_blank" class="auth-soc w-inline-block"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/66b4dcffba1901efd6